PMNCH na-agba mbọ ịkwanyere, ịkwalite na ichekwa ikike na ọdịmma nke mmadụ niile. Echiche ọ bụla ekwuru na nzaghachi nyocha ma ọ bụ ihe ebipụtara na-apụta na dashboard a nke megidere nkwa a, PMNCH akwadoghị.
